    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217690/extras/c6c50c4b32d81034cdd9f907f9d2819a.avif?t=1728930144\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First Break is a relentless action-puzzle game about surviving a strange prison full of traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>In the middle of the night, a masked figure knocks at your door.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an eerie place full of traps and deadly foes. Meet other prisoners, learn the rules of the prison, find its secrets, and navigate through hundreds of rooms in the search of an exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Now, go find a way out. It's ok if you die, but don't ever lose hope.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217690/extras/ab607f86ba22b9882ac8e68469ef3997.webp?t=1728930144\" width=55 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features : </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dozens of challenging levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark and eerie visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unforgiving foes and traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memories hidden in walls and ruins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A haunting soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
